---
// Komponen Harga Zaidly Agency
---

<section id="pricing" class="py-24 bg-[#F8F9FA]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <span class="text-[#7E67F8] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4 block font-mulish">
        Paket Harga
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 font-oswald uppercase leading-tight">
        Pilih Paket <span class="text-[#7E67F8]">Investasi</span> Digital Anda.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 font-mulish">
        Harga transparan tanpa biaya tersembunyi. Pilih yang paling sesuai dengan skala bisnis Anda saat ini.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-sm shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 font-oswald uppercase">Landing Page</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs font-mulish mb-6">Cocok untuk jualan 1 produk/jasa</p>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-oswald italic">Rp 850rb</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            1 Halaman Penjualan
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Copywriting Menjual
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Integrasi WhatsApp
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-400 font-mulish line-through">
            Gratis Artikel SEO
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="block text-center border-2 border-slate-900 text-slate-900 py-4 rounded-sm font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 font-oswald">Pesan Sekarang</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-sm shadow-2xl border-t-4 border-[#7E67F8] relative transform scale-105 z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-[#7E67F8] text-white text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-1">Best Value</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 font-oswald uppercase">Website UMKM</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs font-mulish mb-6">Pilihan paling populer & lengkap</p>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-oswald italic">Rp 1.5jt</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Hingga 5 Halaman
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Domain & Hosting 1 Thn
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Mobile Responsive
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Sitemap & SEO Dasar
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="block text-center bg-[#7E67F8] text-white py-4 rounded-sm font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-slate-900 transition-all duration-300 font-oswald shadow-lg shadow-[#7E67F8]/30">Pesan Sekarang</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-sm shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 font-oswald uppercase">Company Profile</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs font-mulish mb-6">Kredibilitas bisnis tingkat tinggi</p>
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 font-oswald italic">Rp 2.5jt</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Halaman Unlimited
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Email Bisnis (@nama.com)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Full CMS (Bisa Edit Sendiri)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-sm text-slate-600 font-mulish">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#7E67F8] mr-3 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            Keamanan SSL Sertifikat
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="block text-center border-2 border-slate-900 text-slate-900 py-4 rounded-sm font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-slate-900 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 font-oswald">Pesan Sekarang</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>